enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require the conversion of a Date object to a Calendar object, which is a common prerequisite for date comparisons.
The validate method can be used to ensure that the input dates are valid before comparing quarters.
The compareDates method can be invoked before compareQuarters to ensure that the dates are comparable and to provide additional context for the comparison.
The compareMonths method can be invoked before compareQuarters to provide additional context about the month-level comparison, which is a component of the quarter comparison.
